    <sec id="sec6">
      <title>Author Contributions</title>
      <p id="p0100">S.T. and R. Marée conceptualized BIAFLOWS, supervised its implementation, contributed to all technical tasks, and wrote the manuscript. U.R. worked on the core implementation and web user interface of BIAFLOWS with contributions from G.M. and R.H. R. Mormont implemented several modules to interface bioimage analysis workflows and the content of the system. S.T., M.M., and D.Ü. implemented the module to compute benchmark metrics. S.T., V.B., R. Mormont, L.P., B.P., M.M., R.V., and L.A.S. integrated their own workflows or adapted existing workflows, and tested the system. S.T., D.Ü., O.G., and G.B. organized and collected content (image datasets, simulation tools). S.G.S., N.S., and P.P.-G. provided extensive feedback on BIAFLOWS and contributed to the manuscript. All authors took part in reviewing the manuscript.</p>
